<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_8bfb5aa0-67f0-4ce3-bba2-f41c8d49ee93" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>S34C3</sptc><title id="_7996da8b-d942-420f-8392-5e746f46631c">Proposed building and reference building</title><archive-num>2019: Spec JVb: 3</archive-num><subclause id="_10b353c9-62d4-4f7e-aa6b-ddf90875057f" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_a69e364d-ab67-431c-9a37-2d411190df21">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>The <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1188_1.0.0.xml#_eea4a10f-c51b-47b3-ab0b-72043e96d6c8" id="_1ca429f0-da27-468f-bcae-137c94dce1e9" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">annual greenhouse gas emissions</xref> must be calculated for the proposed building and the <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1424_4.10.0.xml#_5dfc40fe-dad0-46ab-9923-f7643beb2160" id="_bbcabd20-1f7e-4cd3-8b53-169159d46e94" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">reference building</xref> using the same—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_dafce7d6-66c8-4e63-96d5-fe4303094646"><xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1188_1.0.0.xml#_eea4a10f-c51b-47b3-ab0b-72043e96d6c8" id="_7693c729-b6fb-4ea3-94ad-2910f1baac73" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">annual greenhouse gas emissions</xref> calculation method; and</li><li id="_4e00286c-54e9-4d5c-8e99-149b74e67208">greenhouse gas emissions factors in accordance with (2); and</li><li id="_d028622d-3e3b-465d-9299-2feb8bed4293">location in accordance with (3); and</li><li id="_5f6402cf-3178-465e-ac74-3f47497c44e2">climatic data, using a projection at year 2050 made under a Representative Concentration Pathway with an 8.5 W/m² increase in radiative forcing; and</li><li id="_e562e7e5-04bb-4932-a2d6-c849afdae328">adjacent structures and features; and</li><li id="_35fb463b-3e64-45f2-9091-ca6f66223a3c">orientation; and</li><li id="_ae715b15-654b-44d3-9d49-345888aae4a4">building form in accordance with (4); and</li><li id="_4eac2657-a647-46d5-9398-6ef77322e08a">testing standards including for insulation, <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1319_2.9.0.xml#_50325745-1d02-4c68-85ac-bd7c1a787b1e" id="_05f7507c-ed84-4297-92bb-68e21972d842" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">glazing</xref>, water heater and unitary <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1181_1.0.0.xml#_386d327a-f182-4f1a-bf21-5cfdef50cc8d" id="_54cd0431-9263-463d-a702-e054db2e06d9" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">air-conditioning</xref> equipment; and</li><li id="_124d6790-86aa-4601-839d-5a0ed448a3be"><xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1269_0.5.0.xml#_9470eb17-f8ba-4a37-9a7e-a343418f0ac7" id="_64af2c14-d966-4de1-a812-1748a1f148c8" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">fabric</xref> and <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1319_2.9.0.xml#_9067b5ce-fa3e-4afd-9b3a-b3520543cb5d" id="_9a01b68d-d6f6-47a5-8626-b6a05103f4bc" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">glazing</xref> in accordance with (5); and</li><li id="_e8b8e3c7-2490-489b-9929-c2747043487d"><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1456_25.0.0.xml#_0eac53b3-4b7c-47cc-8a95-b844822d3d21" id="_a7b161ab-80e0-4af3-8f46-a55aa1db076e" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">services</xref> in accordance with (6) and <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/937_11.11.0.xml#_54a66a48-6836-4069-ad91-8595d208b68e" id="_4df00e9f-dd31-42a4-a9d5-06cfe652d66c" scope="local" type="clause">S34C4</xref>; and</li><li id="_bc85209b-3546-48c9-91b9-f5f22a1c8348">target for thermal comfort minimums as per <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/3372_3.23.0.xml#_d889e8e0-0757-4009-92d5-d595375d6be0" id="_5e7c6153-483e-44bd-beb8-3fc41807175f" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="subclause">J1V3(1)(b)</xref>.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_03d04780-cf23-47fa-a988-4482cb3f7117" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_77975c70-1cb0-41d5-846c-478865b1842e">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>For the purposes of (1)(b), greenhouse gas emissions factors must be based on the factors in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/233_0.16.0.xml#_ec4006ea-721c-467f-917f-a7ace2f658e1" id="_26fc4660-9833-4da4-8132-267e9b6f2f22" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">Table S34C3</xref>. </p></subclause><subclause id="_1d3b6632-8bac-4e7b-b2c8-1ae13178b093" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_75c1ec42-b3bb-40bb-a39e-2ec86a49c60a">SubClause</title><num>3</num><p>For the purposes of (1)(c), location must be either—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_8f1d031e-c306-43a9-a5e7-e85656f1afb6">the location where the building is to be constructed if appropriate climatic data is available; or</li><li id="_bdbc6a7a-e852-470f-ad0c-90b8f2f3d360">the nearest location with similar climatic conditions, for which climatic data is available.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_8c403911-6fb6-4f56-bbad-ff2c78470245" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_ecf36335-7833-48a2-b976-a3a882350d8c">SubClause</title><num>4</num><p>For the purposes of (1)(g), building form must include the same—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_4730f89b-3678-4741-a408-4a54830095d8">roof geometry; and</li><li id="_0ca921b1-d2a1-4945-a41e-34db5be42e47">floor plan; and</li><li id="_f66aef5a-c41e-4379-8de1-fdc5a5517b41">number of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1483_25.0.0.xml#_53ff3ea1-55e7-4f2a-b2b3-ca445ff64c15" id="_3302d985-650c-4154-9004-4a677baa34ce" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">storeys</xref>; and</li><li id="_14a2883f-df34-4fb3-a177-50f0d6291aec">location, extent and configuration of ground floors and basements; and</li><li id="_1ce84329-69d1-46fd-9bd6-891d68031aae">size and location of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1319_2.9.0.xml#_50325745-1d02-4c68-85ac-bd7c1a787b1e" id="_3e9e5f8c-1b09-4bac-bef4-de58be94877f" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">glazing</xref>; and</li><li id="_f808aaad-9bdd-45f6-903d-2068e5a03d4d">external doors.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_584992f1-0a02-4d8d-af25-74e2a89b0588" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_51bbdf4e-b070-42cb-a6c6-fbe9edfabe7e">SubClause</title><num>5</num><p>For the purposes of (1)(i), fabric and <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1319_2.9.0.xml#_50325745-1d02-4c68-85ac-bd7c1a787b1e" id="_437f8fe6-3426-410c-84cc-aaf436eb3274" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">glazing</xref> must include the same—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_081b6d62-67b6-4a1d-a2f6-acb9ce9fc971">thermal resistance of air films including any adjustment factors, moisture content of materials and the like; and</li><li id="_521b355f-5af0-41fb-b26f-736522d043a8">dimensions of external, internal and separating walls; and</li><li id="_901f94d2-a821-458f-a9fe-e25fd9aeec5a">internal shading devices, including their colour and their criteria for operation; and</li><li id="_6ee8dc28-fdea-4500-9ec0-22f3b314dae6">location and extent of thermal mass.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_a01b255f-6b36-4c3c-915f-a8aabbcbceed" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_b442c669-7608-4034-90bb-19361d3d6b2d">SubClause</title><num>6</num><p>For the purposes of (1)(j), <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1456_25.0.0.xml#_0eac53b3-4b7c-47cc-8a95-b844822d3d21" id="_672958b1-e995-4c80-ac60-7e56138a9213" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">services</xref> must include the same—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_3ff39add-219b-4582-a7ec-a697dd878cee">range and type of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1456_25.0.0.xml#_242ba975-4cdf-4b84-9f41-b8d524ee17c2" id="_414e6d69-266e-4662-948c-1ebde4b16bc4" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">services</xref> and energy sources including the same proportions and functions of air-cooled and water-cooled <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1181_1.0.0.xml#_386d327a-f182-4f1a-bf21-5cfdef50cc8d" id="_7615a188-cf8b-4e55-877d-63ddd29c7fba" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">air-conditioning</xref> equipment; and</li><li id="_b98226be-c186-4ba9-a15a-7047711d77aa"><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1181_1.0.0.xml#_386d327a-f182-4f1a-bf21-5cfdef50cc8d" id="_a00b3853-095d-491e-acab-2f14013a6996" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">air-conditioning</xref> zones including—<ol><li>separate zones for each <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1483_25.0.0.xml#_53ff3ea1-55e7-4f2a-b2b3-ca445ff64c15" id="_bcf39b40-17a4-47ba-af9e-5c8a63265139" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">storey</xref>; and</li><li>separate zones for each <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1473_0.4.0.xml#_d2c89488-8a36-464b-94f6-a91d0f5a6c9c" id="_21767c6a-24e7-43f3-9e26-31d1eaedbd2b" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">sole-occupancy unit</xref>; and</li><li>in spaces larger than 20 m², separate perimeter zones, no deeper than 4 m adjacent to <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1267_2.3.0.xml#_d87c7cc0-d0b0-40ab-9a5b-d070ed6e115e" id="_a1e1dfef-a7a9-4a5f-9eb1-c52086bc7a67" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">external walls</xref> with windows facing—<ol><li>within 45° of true north; and</li><li>within 45° of true south; and</li><li>within 45° of true east; and</li><li>within 45° of true west; and</li></ol></li><li>separate centre zones comprising the remainder of each <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1473_0.4.0.xml#_d2c89488-8a36-464b-94f6-a91d0f5a6c9c" id="_6a47b52b-985c-4a52-8b95-6d7355ece617" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">sole-occupancy unit</xref> within each <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1483_25.0.0.xml#_53ff3ea1-55e7-4f2a-b2b3-ca445ff64c15" id="_f4133aeb-efe7-4399-9a8a-de04119a2fb5" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">storey</xref>; and</li><li>the same method of calculating the temperature difference across <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1181_1.0.0.xml#_386d327a-f182-4f1a-bf21-5cfdef50cc8d" id="_59bdf423-ee9b-474b-9a63-8e2ad7f606e8" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">air-conditioning</xref> zone boundaries; and</li><li>the same method of combining zones with similar heating and cooling requirements, where necessary to simplify the simulation; and</li></ol></li><li id="_f1ff4c55-a962-48af-97c6-3e9b13d7c451">floor coverings and furniture and fittings density; and</li><li id="_dcf8a5c4-69c2-4f98-a874-64cdc483fa9c">internal artificial lighting illumination levels; and</li><li id="_228c6fc6-0346-4cb7-b8cf-f4bcef92d660">internal heat gains including people, lighting, appliances, meals and other electric power loads; and</li><li id="_17ee9380-a0e0-4bdd-9e7a-8b7ed3b2db29"><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1181_1.0.0.xml#_386d327a-f182-4f1a-bf21-5cfdef50cc8d" id="_60651c70-c42f-4d6d-9dbe-e6584d3a5632" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">air-conditioning</xref>, including chiller, fan and <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1210_0.10.0.xml#_e687404d-1eb3-41fe-9e90-2b307fb562e7" id="_69b0e555-b729-4050-bd13-9a1765ddbfbb" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">boiler</xref> equipment, system configuration; and</li><li id="_45d5edf1-fa7d-46b8-92a7-9886ee253075">profiles for occupancy, <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1181_1.0.0.xml#_386d327a-f182-4f1a-bf21-5cfdef50cc8d" id="_b2faa086-4c43-4b9a-bee8-9dc0937d336f" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">air-conditioning</xref>, lighting and internal heat gains from people, hot meals, appliances, equipment and heated water supply systems based on—<ol><li><xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1142_0.7.0.xml#_22039b4c-3303-4948-97ae-d7202aaa57bf" id="_9fccb37a-27a0-48c9-bd6b-8c66a00a9257" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="specification">Specification 35</xref>; or</li><li><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1375_0.6.0.xml#_ec872d9e-d88d-4372-9d60-43327a3cb139" id="_7ce2f079-e5fc-4c1e-8a80-808a232ba622" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">NABERS Energy</xref> simulation requirements; or</li><li><xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1322_0.4.0.xml#_59b54ff5-6934-4bc5-aca4-fedfd859b96b" id="_d5d8c98a-75e2-44bf-9572-15b6445ce255" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">Green Star</xref> simulation requirements; or</li><li>the actual building if—<ol><li>the operating hours per year are not less than 2,500; or</li><li>the daily operating profiles are not listed in <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1142_0.7.0.xml#_22039b4c-3303-4948-97ae-d7202aaa57bf" id="_df4662a4-3ef2-4a57-bda2-e12f1ab4ef99" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="specification">Specification 35</xref>; and</li></ol></li></ol></li><li id="_2f355944-2c10-4bad-94d1-bf0bf3e226ed">supply heated water temperature and rate of use; and</li><li id="_d1e82168-92ba-4389-8400-7aa49278f30c">infiltration values, subject to (7); and</li><li id="_3963c0be-3c64-41ed-9947-f7f613de699c">sequencing for water heaters, refrigeration chillers and heat rejection equipment such as cooling towers; and</li><li id="_afbbbea1-d1db-43dc-a161-ab4e9b0e7d66">where <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/3372_3.23.0.xml#_96c5d91c-f777-41e6-b560-7d2ca07e87ee" id="_5b27b626-368a-4a3a-9f81-181bf2b0ca0a" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">J1V3(1)(b)(i)</xref> applies, representation of clothing and metabolic rate of the occupants, and air speed from mechanical services; and</li><li id="_3d729090-72fa-428b-8faf-f0317910927c">control of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1181_1.0.0.xml#_386d327a-f182-4f1a-bf21-5cfdef50cc8d" id="_f89bb41d-aea4-4cb5-90ea-3204ce7e99bb" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">air-conditioning</xref>, in accordance with the requirements of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/138_0.29.0.xml#_05bbc3db-9aa4-4fd6-b2a2-0a5551074b52" id="_47441ec5-bcda-4fa7-b376-1ca7f5d465d4" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-part">Part J6</xref>, except if the controls for the proposed building are not adequately specified or cannot be simulated, the sample control specifications in Appendix B of AIRAH-DA28 must be used; and</li><li id="_c94406cc-4498-477b-bd6e-648e88853d6e">environmental conditions such as ground reflectivity, form factors for topography and built environment, temperature of external bounding surfaces, air velocities across external surfaces, vegetation and the like; and</li><li id="_ca694a60-ba5a-4ff4-84fa-8580dc6901da">number, sizes, floors and traffic served by lifts and escalators; and</li><li id="_5a9dc734-98e4-49bc-b7d2-2d8f74a6e574">loss factors for solar PV installation.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_8f4ab0cb-a4ba-4492-88fc-8d594025b6c9" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_d2e603c0-734c-4504-adfb-23496e603850">SubClause</title><num>7</num><p>For the purposes of (6)(i), the intended building leakage at 50 Pa may be converted into a whole building infiltration value for the proposed building infiltration using Tables 4.16 to 4.24 of CIBSE Guide A if all of the following have been specified:</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_e8d2a979-19b8-4afd-b70d-c93eceb29bff">Additional sealing provisions to those <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_c231d2be-1e51-40e6-9d2f-0e06013bc6ba" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> by <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/3404_0.30.0.xml#_3aaf1df9-dc92-448e-86ee-c469d1fe194e" id="_57eb72f6-579a-4a7b-b6fb-fdfdfc02053b" scope="local" type="part">Part J5</xref>.</li><li id="_286a821f-261d-42f8-a3cf-9826c845a948">An intended building leakage of less than 10 m<sup id="_8c6ef205-a602-4b8c-b5a6-66f6f7a9c4da">3</sup>/hr.m<sup id="_37a6d8c4-f30b-445d-acdf-15b1c39e1b7a">2</sup> at 50 Pa.</li><li id="_d316309c-0ad0-427f-afd9-175b49fb9e09">Pressure testing to verify achievement of the intended building leakage.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_e6201632-9bff-422e-b121-ce7b8dabac6d" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_32bc997b-80b6-4c1b-bc57-a0c6f8bb8f1a">SubClause</title><num>8</num><p>Where <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/3372_3.23.0.xml#_d889e8e0-0757-4009-92d5-d595375d6be0" id="_ad892095-4446-4ea7-bbb7-76215317ca53" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="subclause">J1V3(1)(b)(iii)</xref>, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/3372_3.23.0.xml#_d889e8e0-0757-4009-92d5-d595375d6be0" id="_65a475e5-aaad-4fb7-8498-cbbdb6b91c16" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="subclause">(iv)</xref> or <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/3372_3.23.0.xml#_d889e8e0-0757-4009-92d5-d595375d6be0" id="_0f2024a2-3271-4944-942d-d4ab4b50e558" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="subclause">(v)</xref> applies, the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1181_1.0.0.xml#_386d327a-f182-4f1a-bf21-5cfdef50cc8d" id="_68968461-4ea6-4aa6-8ca8-0983fd73d635" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">air-conditioning</xref> must—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_d2acaf3b-8162-494b-8303-a12ebb73e39a">subject to (b), for 95% of the annual hours of operation, achieve dry bulb temperatures between—<ol><li>18°C to 25°C for <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1225_1.8.0.xml#_26276791-20ad-4404-951f-29b5bff0ff80" id="_cf43835e-6ef1-4a66-bc18-a29898830ff1" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">conditioned spaces</xref> with transitory occupancy; and</li><li>21°C to 24°C in all other <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1225_1.8.0.xml#_26276791-20ad-4404-951f-29b5bff0ff80" id="_e8065add-777e-4192-9c6c-d3fb02dece0b" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">conditioned spaces</xref>; and</li></ol></li><li id="_ad924490-5605-4007-ae28-d3102beb8b1f">if the proposed building has no mechanically provided cooling or has mixed mode cooling, the proposed building and reference building must have the same method of control and control set points for non-mechanical cooling.</li></ol></subclause><table-reference conref="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/233_0.16.0.xml" graph="None" id="_ec4006ea-721c-467f-917f-a7ace2f658e1"><num/><title id="_2d7ef230-a0ed-489b-b371-9bb8e884b793"/></table-reference></clause>